#: ../../pointers.md:1
msgid "Data pointers"
msgstr "数据指针"

#: ../../pointers.md:3
msgid "How pointers are used"
msgstr "如何使用指针"

#: ../../pointers.md:5
msgid ""
"In C, pointer arguments are used for differenty purposes. It is important"
" to distinguish these use cases because Koffi provides different ways to "
"deal with each of them:"
msgstr ""
"在C中, 指针参数有多种用途. 区分这些用例很重要, Koffi提供了不同的方法来处理它们:"

#: ../../pointers.md:7
msgid ""
"**Struct pointers**: Use of struct pointers by C libraries fall in two "
"cases: avoid (potentially) expensive copies, and to let the function "
"change struct contents (output or input/output arguments)."
msgstr ""
"**结构体指针**: C库中使用结构体指针通常用于两种情况: (一定程度上)避免昂贵的复制成本, 以及允许函数修改结构体的内容(输出或输入/输出参数)."

#: ../../pointers.md:8
msgid ""
"**Opaque pointers**: the library does not expose the contents of the "
"structs, and only provides you with a pointer to it (e.g. `FILE *`). Only"
" the functions provided by the library can do something with this "
"pointer, in Koffi we call this an opaque type. This is usually done for "
"ABI-stability reason, and to prevent library users from messing directly "
"with library internals."
msgstr ""
"**不透明指针**: 库并不暴露结构体中的成员, 且仅提供给你它的指针(例如`File *`). 只有库提供的函数可以操作这个指针, 这种情况下Koffi将其成为不透明类型. "
"这通常处于ABI稳定方面的考虑, 且阻止库的使用者直接破坏库的内部组织."

#: ../../pointers.md:9
msgid ""
"**Pointers to primitive types**: This is more rare, and generally used "
"for output or input/output arguments. The Win32 API has a lot of these."
msgstr ""
"**原生类型指针**: 这更加罕见, 通常用于输出或输入/输出参数. Win32 API中大量使用了这种模式."

#: ../../pointers.md:10
msgid ""
"**Arrays**: in C, you dynamically-sized arrays are usually passed to "
"functions with pointers, either NULL-terminated (or any other sentinel "
"value) or with an additional length argument."
msgstr ""
"**数组**: 在C中, 你的变长数组通常以指针的形式传给函数, 要么是NULL结尾(或是其他特定值), 要么附带一个额外的长度参数."

#: ../../pointers.md:12
msgid "Pointer types"
msgstr "指针类型"

#: ../../pointers.md:14
msgid "Struct pointers"
msgstr "结构体指针"

#: ../../pointers.md:16
msgid ""
"The following Win32 example uses `GetCursorPos()` (with an output "
"parameter) to retrieve and show the current cursor position."
msgstr ""
"下面的Win32例子使用了`GetCursorPos()`(包含一个输出参数)来获取并显示当前的鼠标坐标."

#: ../../pointers.md:40
msgid "Opaque pointers"
msgstr "不透明指针"

#: ../../pointers.md:42 ../../pointers.md:137
msgid "*New in Koffi 2.0*"
msgstr "*Koffi 2.0引入*"

#: ../../pointers.md:44
msgid ""
